  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243700/extras/c396cbfb64a43496fb95d25aa304e17c.poster.avif?t=1725164804\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243700/extras/c396cbfb64a43496fb95d25aa304e17c.webm?t=1725164804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243700/extras/c396cbfb64a43496fb95d25aa304e17c.mp4?t=1725164804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>十年前，长安路<br>观音问：你为何礼佛？<br>我答：为这盛世。<br>观音问：既是盛世，何人需度？<br>我无言以对。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243700/extras/5511781b11182fcba461bf1919eb4a8a.poster.avif?t=1725164804\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243700/extras/5511781b11182fcba461bf1919eb4a8a.webm?t=1725164804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243700/extras/5511781b11182fcba461bf1919eb4a8a.mp4?t=1725164804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>十年后，那烂陀前<br>观音问：此去西天，若一去不回，该如何？<br>我答：若一去不回，便一去不回。<br><br>一世，我化作猢狲，屠尽鬼魅，杀穿西天路，大日如来前，败。<br>二世，我化作猪猡，纵横捭阖，运筹铜臭中，大日如来前，败。<br>三世，我化作龟鳖，一路奉引，好友遍九天，大日如来前，败。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243700/extras/1ace9de54d54c569e2e2ede4df915003.avif?t=1725164804\" width=616 height=202 /></span><br>我问观音：我为何缕败？<br>观音问：<br>败？你可指高老庄弃翠兰之情？<br>败？你可指火焰山弃文泰之义？<br>败？你可指车迟国弃小儿之命？<br>我仍无言以对。<br><br>观音拈花，我竟微笑。<br>便重新踏上这无尽的善恶之旅。<br><br>官方QQ群:142283512",
